-110; Wang, E., Engel, T., Simulation of phenological development of wheat crops (1998) Agricultural Systems, 58, pp. 1-24; Weiss, A., Hays, C.J., Won, J., Assessing winter wheat responses to climate change scenarios: a simulation study in the U.S. Great Plains (2003) Climatic Change, 58, pp. 119-147","Lago, I.; Universidade Federal de Santa Maria, Centro de Ciências Rurais, Departamento de Fitotecnia, CEP, 97105-900 Santa Maria, RS, Brazil; email: isalago08@yahoo.com.br",,,,,,,,0100204X,,,,"English; Portuguese","Pesqui. Agropecu. Bras.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-65249180651
